---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Cyber-Brief"
  description="Privacy policy for Cyber-Brief — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <Nav />

  <div>
    <div class="legal-wrap">

      <div class="page-header">
        <div class="page-eyebrow">
          <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
          <span class="eyebrow-text">Legal</span>
        </div>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: March 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you subscribe to Cyber-Brief, we collect your email address. This is the only personal information we collect. We do not collect names, phone numbers, payment information, or any other personal data.</p>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Your email address is used solely to deliver Cyber-Brief intelligence briefings to your inbox. We do not sell, rent, or share your email address with any third party for marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2>Email Communications</h2>
        <p>By subscribing, you consent to receive periodic intelligence briefings from Cyber-Brief. Every email we send includes an unsubscribe link. You may opt out at any time and your email will be removed from our list immediately.</p>

        <h2>Data Storage</h2>
        <p>Subscriber email addresses are stored securely via Netlify Forms. Netlify's privacy policy governs how form submission data is stored and processed on their platform.</p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>Cyber-Brief uses a single cookie to remember your display preference (light or dark mode). This cookie contains no personal information and is stored only on your device. No tracking cookies or third-party analytics cookies are used.</p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>Cyber-Brief does not use advertising networks, tracking pixels, or third-party analytics services. We do not participate in behavioral advertising of any kind.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to request deletion of your email address from our subscriber list at any time. To do so, use the unsubscribe link in any email or contact us directly.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this privacy policy may be directed to Cyber Edge LLC via the contact information on our About page.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-wrap { padding-bottom: 80px; }

  .page-header {
    padding: 80px 0 48px;
    max-width: 680px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .page-eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .eyebrow-line {
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--coral);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .eyebrow-text {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--heading);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .legal-content {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .legal-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading);
    margin: 40px 0 14px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .legal-content h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

  .legal-content p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--body-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }
</style>